Micex to Offer Currency Trading to All Companies, RBC Reports

-- B y   Y u l i y a   F e d o r i n o v a
-- 
2011-12-06T06:52:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-06/micex-to-offer-currency-trading-to-all-companies-rbc-reports.html
Micex exchange plans to offer
 currency trading  to all companies after it merges with smaller
Russian competitor RTS,  RBC Daily  reported, citing Micex Vice
President Igor Marich.  Only banks can trade currency on the exchange now, the
newspaper reported today. The change will probably take effect
next December, RBC said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yuliya Fedorinova in Moscow at 
 yfedorinova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  